The '''Masterball''' is a type of pokeball. It automatically tries to catch a wild Pokémon after defeating it if and is the highest type of pokeball avaliable.


==Details==
===Description===
The Ultimate pokeball to capture Pokémon with. It has an 100% catch rate.

